# go-read-PrivateStorage


## Format
```
Slot 0 (32 bytes):
+---------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| Padding       | startTime        | user                          |
| (4 bytes)     | (8 bytes)        | (20 bytes)                    |
+---------------+------------------+-------------------------------+

Slot 1 (32 bytes):
+------------------------------------------------------------------+
| amount                                                           |
| (32 bytes)                                                       |
+------------------------------------------------------------------+
```
